api_list.description:
If response contains an error code with response body

``` json
{
    code: 'BANK_STATEMENT_REQUIRED'    
}

```

Upload Bank Statement using [Businesses -> Upload Bank Statement](https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/9478456/TzRYe5Mf#c26224de-9de1-4810-accd-a937e4af2837) to the Bank marked as

``` json
{
    is_for_nach: true
}

```

and retry Send to LOS.

